						<div class="postbody">For the sake of simplicity, I had meant to constrain this thread to just background scrolling. I don't care as much about sprite popping because that's so brief and near the edge of the screen. But if the whole updated row of a nametable is visible you have a veritable light show on your hands. So, if I end up perfecting any of those issues, it will be scrolling.</div>

